OL,3,CSex workers in Belgium to access paid
OL,4,Cleave and pensions after new law
OL,6,FBelgian sex workers will be able to
OL,7,Faccess a range of employment rights
OL,8,Fincluding health insurance, paid leave
OL,9,Fand maternity benefits, according to a
OL,10,Fnew law coming into force on Sunday.
OL,12,FThe legal breakthrough also
OL,13,Festablishes fundamental rights for sex
OL,14,Fworkers including the right to refuse
OL,15,Fclients, choose their practices and
OL,16,Fstop an act at any moment.
OL,18,FSex workers will be able to receive
OL,19,Funemployment support, and rules on
OL,20,Fworking hours, pay and safety measures
OL,21,Fwill be introduced.
