OL,3,CSex workers in Belgium to access paid
OL,4,Cleave and pensions after new law
OL,6,FWhile countries such as Germany and
OL,7,Fthe Netherlands have legalized sex
OL,8,Fwork, none have implemented labor
OL,9,Fprotections as comprehensive as
OL,10,FBelgium's new laws.
OL,12,FThose employing sex workers must now
OL,13,Flegally provide clean linens, condoms,
OL,14,Fand hygiene products, and install
OL,15,Femergency buttons in workspaces.
OL,17,FIsabelle Jaramillo, coordinator of
OL,18,FEspace P, an advocacy group involved
OL,19,Fin drafting the legislation, said:
OL,20,F"This is an incredible step forward.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
