OL,6,F"Under the previous legislation,
OL,7,Fhiring someone for sex work
OL,8,Fautomatically made you a pimp, even if
OL,9,Fthe arrangement was consensual. Now,
OL,10,FThey'll have to apply for state
OL,11,Fauthorisation to hire employees."
