OL,3,CSex workers in Belgium to access paid
OL,4,Cleave and pensions after new law
OL,6,FEmployers must now obtain
OL,7,Fauthorisation, adhere to strict safety
OL,8,Fprotocols, and meet background
OL,9,Frequirements, including no prior
OL,10,Fconvictions for sexual assault or
OL,11,Fhuman trafficking.
OL,13,FCritics argue the law cannot fully
OL,14,Faddress the stigma and risks tied to
OL,15,Fthe trade, especially for undocumented
OL,16,Fsex workers.
